snippet.title: Note Ban: Things to Remember while Making a Cashless Transaction

localized.description:
Note Ban: Things to remember while making a cashless transaction. Indian banking systems are prone to cyber attacks and customers are prone to frauds. Amid demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes peoples are using e-wallets, debit or credit cards and other methods for payments.
